







       A Scale should be used to select a value from a range.  This
       component should be composed of a slider, moving within an
       element that indicates the size of the range, called the
       trough, and a label that indicates the current value.  The
       position of the slider that indicates the value relative to
       the range.  A Scale can also have buttons with arrow graph-
       ics for moving the slider.












       The following text describes the operations of this com-
       ponent.

